Company Introduction



                                    ORIENT INTERNATIONAL ENTERPRISE Ltd. (OIE) became a public company in July 2000, since its estab- lishment in November 1998. The registered capital of OIE is RMB 320 million yuan. White the core advantage remains textiles and apparels, its business scope actually covers international trading of all kinds of commodity and service. As a successor of former Shanghai Gar- ments Imp. &. Exp. Co. ...
                                

                                        ORIENT INTERNATIONAL ENTERPRISE Ltd. (OIE) became a public company in July 2000, since its estab- lishment in November 1998. The registered capital of OIE is RMB 320 million yuan. 

White the core advantage remains textiles and apparels, its business scope actually covers international trading of all kinds of commodity and service. As a successor of former Shanghai Gar- ments Imp. &. Exp. Co. Which had engaged in foreign trade business for 4 decades, OIE is now one of the subsidiaries of ORIENT INTERNATIONAL HOLDING (OIH). By the end of 2006, OIE's asset totals to RMB 2.3 billion yuan with net asset of RMB 1.0 billion yuan. 

Manufacturing bases --Three manufacturing-oriented subsidiary factories under company's direct control with ample capacity and modem facilities.
                                    


