Orient International Enterprise, Ltd. Key Developments

Orient International Enterprise Ltd. Announces Implementation of Rights and Interests Distribution in 2016, Payable on July 14, 2017
Jul 5 17
Orient International Enterprise, Ltd. announced the cash dividend of RMB 0.09 (taxes included) per A share under the scheme of rights and interests distribution in 2016. The cash dividend will be paid on July 14, 2017 to the shareholders with the record date as on July 13, 2017. The Ex-dividend date is July 14, 2017.


Orient International Enterprise, Ltd. Reports Earnings Results for the First Quarter of 2017
Apr 21 17
Orient International Enterprise, Ltd. reported earnings results for the first quarter of 2017. For the quarter, the company reported basic earnings per share of CNY 0.09 and weighted average return on net assets of 1.28%.


Orient International Enterprise, Ltd., Annual General Meeting, May 18, 2017
Apr 21 17
Orient International Enterprise, Ltd., Annual General Meeting, May 18, 2017. Agenda: To consider the issues including the annual report of 2016; to consider the scheme of profit distribution of 2016; and to consider the proposal of engaging accounting firm and deciding its audit fee of 2017.


